text: Hubert Clompe (22 July 1910 - 30 December 1995) was a Romanian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Romanian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Romania Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brașov
